* 瓦爾韋德在將打者三振出局或解決後，會以較為誇張的姿勢來表示，或直接振臂握拳怒吼，時而引起對手的不滿，並引發一些爭議<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120612/56407.htm |title=MLB／球已經夠快　老虎終結者偷吐口水在球上？ |accessdate=2013-08-13 |archive-date=2012-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120910203720/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120612/56407.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://detroit.tigers.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110818&content_id=23394566&c_id=det Valverde: Part showman, part shutdown]{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。前隊友[[米格爾·蒙特羅|米格爾·蒙特羅]]對此亦有微詞<ref>[http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jspymd=20100620&content_id=11389732&notebook_id=11394516&vkey=notebook_ari&fext=.jsp&c_id=ari Ex-mates Montero, Valverde trade barbs] MLB.com. 2010-06-20.</ref><ref>[http://www.azcentral.com/sports/diamondbacks/articles/2010/06/20/20100620tigers-valverde-rips-diamondbacks-montero.html Jose Valverde rips Miguel Montero, blasts Diamondbacks] ''Arizona Now''. 2010-06-20.</ref>。

